column10: Sometimes there are to many buses that they block the drivers vision. The buses also block the crosswalk.

There is a 5 inch gap in the pavement on the bridge that caused me to lose balance on my bike and fall down in the midst of car traffic going both ways. There is no bike lane. I broke my hip in the fall and went to hospital in an ambulance.
